title: Cozy apartment available for rent on August 12
neighborhood: 6455 Zane Ave N, Minneapolis / St Paul, MN
posting_body: ['Eden Park Apartments is nestled in the heart of Brooklyn Park, MN and surrounded by award-winning parks, lakes, and trails.', 'We are just 15 minutes to downtown Minneapolis from I-694 and I-35W and less than 3 miles from Shoppes at Arbor Lakes, Crystal Shopping Center (near Bass Lake Road and Broadway Avenue) and plenty of everyday conveniences.', 'You can walk to get coffee at Mad Jacks Sports Cafe, Egg House Cafe, and buy groceries at Fast N Fresh Foods.', 'Eden Park offers 1, 2, and 3 bedroom apartments for rent.', 'Our buildings are three story walk ups with beautiful garden views from each patio or balcony.', 'Our Brooklyn Park apartments feature updated kitchens, large windows, and spacious closets.', 'Regardless of your needs, our dedicated leasing staff is eager to assist you and show you a better style of living!', 'We look forward to scheduling your personalized tour of your new home!', 'Take a relaxing dip in our outdoor swimming pool or exercise at our fully equipped on-site fitness center.', 'We also have a playground and several laundry facilities on the property.', 'We are conveniently located to highways and public transportation.', 'Our community combines quality apartments, wonderful location, and excellent management to create a great rental experience.', 'Our staff is here to serve you and create an enjoyable rental experience.', 'Welcome
